thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Tuan Anh Pham

author: Tuan Anh Pham
title: Tuan Anh Pham
text: I have purchases several products and I really satisfy with all of them. The customer service is excellent, too. When my order was returned to the warehouse by the postal service because I couldn't present on time of delivery for signature, they offered to resend the order to me without any charge.
